    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "i had this weird thing happen today at work. my boss was telling me about the new project timeline but i could literally feel this weird vibration in my chest every time he spoke. it was like a low, discordant frequency that just felt... wrong. i'm almost certain he was lying to me about the deadline. has anyone else ever described feeling things like that?",
